data.description: ASSUMABLE LOAN!! *Brand New Roof*Patio home conveniently situated in a quiet cult-de-sac. Freshly painted and new carpet installed. If privacy and views are something that you haven't been able to find, here you go! From your fully fenced backyard you can see the expansive Rock Creek Park and unobstructed views of the mountains! Located near the new Legacy entrance makes commuting anywhere a breeze. Landscaped with auto sprinklers and flat terrain, you won't be wasting weekends mowing. Glen Eagle Golf course is located around the corner! Inside you will find a large kitchen with a built in desk and ample storage. A vaulted great room that also views the mountains with a gas fireplace to get cozy by in the winter. The master features a garden soaking tub. Two more good size bedrooms and another full bath to complete this cute one owner patio home! All information to be verified by the buyer.
